Hello again everybody.
Here is my second surf_uhs map and its **really**
different from the first one. On the one side I fixed
the style and on the other i created new surfways.
I hope you enjoy it like I do.

Also there are some secrets now. If you want to know
them, just write me. But they aren't too hard to find.

Good luck & much fun!
Hansoba
